{"tid":2095584,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★智能手機業務遇阻滯   華為傳進軍電腦屏幕市場","createTime":"2020-07-05T14:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T15:37:10.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"188f285757f6c39d995880551f78a87e54b52968","tid":2095584,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:40:35.000Z","msg":"被美國納入實體清單的華為，在通訊設備和智能手機業務上遇到不少阻滯，日前有消息指華為將會進軍另一領域，未知是否與上述事件有關。微博用戶@長安數碼君爆料指，華為的電腦屏幕要來了，而且還涵蓋高、中、低階 3 個市場定位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有大陸傳媒表示網民爆料與早前的傳聞脗合，指華為電腦屏幕已經經過了超過一年的測試，將會有 3 個版本，預計會在未來數月內發表。當中一款屏幕為 32 吋，使用類似 mini LED 背光 512 或 1,024 分區，華為將會加入支援自家品牌其他數碼產品，例如手機和平板的特殊功能。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/07/05/huawei-monitor-series-coming-soon/wireless-home/desktop-pc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F07%2F05%2Fhuawei-monitor-series-coming-soon%2Fwireless-home%2Fdesktop-pc%2F&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj3yWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=0fcb66f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/07/05/huawei-monitor-series-coming-soon/wireless-home/desktop-pc/</a>"},{"pid":"ae5765bd8053d828290f1cd8b2f6c28150e4eeaa","tid":2095584,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b98a6c578568cd856ccb521ecfc397c23cb1a36","tid":2095584,"uid":156891,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:48:11.000Z","msg":"肯定出埋d連cam連收音咪做賣點既mon"},{"pid":"5978751d15e862d8694a07bd6a12e25ab0fbd163","tid":2095584,"uid":5686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b98a6c578568cd856ccb521ecfc397c23